	var sizeScrollBar = 20;
	var images = [];
	var max = null;
	
	images.push({img: '', formatMin: 1920});
	images.push({img: '', formatMin: 1440});
	images.push({img: 'https://tpc.googlesyndication.com/simgad/7163144987234080021?', formatMin: 200});
	
	images = images.filter(function(item) {return item.img !== '';});
	
	var baseStyles = &quot;&quot; +
		&quot;@media (max-width: 768px) {\n&quot; +
			&quot;\t.gg-ad-img {\n&quot; +
				&quot;\t\theight: 188px !important;\n&quot; +
			&quot;\t}\n&quot; +
		&quot;}\n\n&quot; +

			&quot;\tdisplay: block; width: 100%; height: 250px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center; background-size: contain;\n&quot; +
		&quot;}\n&quot;;
	
	var stylesContent = images.map(function(item, i) {
		var style = &quot;@media screen and (min-width: &quot; + (item.formatMin - sizeScrollBar) + &quot;px) &quot; + (max ? &quot; and (max-width: &quot; + (max - sizeScrollBar) + &quot;px)&quot; : &quot;&quot;)  + &quot; {\n&quot; +
			&quot;\t.gg-ad-img {\n&quot; +

			&quot;\t}\n&quot; +
		&quot;}\n\n&quot;;
		max = item.formatMin - 1;
		return style;
	});
	
	var head = document.querySelector('head');
    var styles = document.createElement('style');
	styles.innerHTML = baseStyles + stylesContent.join(&quot;&quot;);
